               <msContents>
                  <summary>Enoch, መጽሐፈ፡ ሄኖክ፡ (ff. 1r-32v); Isaiah (33r-64v); 1 col of excerpt from
                     Jer cyc (65r); Daniel cyc (65r-78r); History of the Israelite Kings, (መጽሐፈ
                     ኅፁፃን) in two books, Book 1 ( in 29 chapters, ff.78r -98r) and Book 2 (in 37
                     chapters, ff. 98r-122v) </summary>
